2fc1678a-a95e-4ad6-b5fc-befa144e923c.title: Draul Leptoc
2fc1678a-a95e-4ad6-b5fc-befa144e923c.text:
What are you doing in my house...why the
impertinence...the sheer cheek...how dare you violate my
personal lodgings....

33a03a0a-fef3-4c44-bd51-311e3e12c51a.title: Draul Leptoc
33a03a0a-fef3-4c44-bd51-311e3e12c51a.text:
Well get out! Get out....this is my house....and don't go
near my daughter Juliet...she's grounded in her room
to keep her away from that good for nothing Romeo.

4fdff04b-3864-4752-9dbd-1130b51d6a15.title: Draul Leptoc
4fdff04b-3864-4752-9dbd-1130b51d6a15.text: What are you doing here? Snooping around...

options.text: I've come to see Juliet on Romeo's behalf.
I've just come to have a chat with Juliet.

ccf710bd-683e-41c4-b671-15faa17d822b.title: <player>
ccf710bd-683e-41c4-b671-15faa17d822b.text: I've come to see Juliet on Romeo's behalf.

f22c5a01-f92c-4447-bb05-f32e1aa18b68.title: Draul Leptoc
f22c5a01-f92c-4447-bb05-f32e1aa18b68.text:
What...what...Romeo! Why that good for nothing
swine...he's always trying to get the affections of my
daughter..that soppy, half brained nincompoop won't ever
have the heart of my daughter.

00cc2c9f-75fa-4f3f-95be-3f19aa7fbd64.title: Draul Leptoc
00cc2c9f-75fa-4f3f-95be-3f19aa7fbd64.text: She deserves someone of character, wit and repose.

e347f766-8e38-4feb-8106-b8e118e50459.title: Draul Leptoc
e347f766-8e38-4feb-8106-b8e118e50459.text:
Wrong! What's wrong with him...have you actually
talked to him? He's nothing but a dim witted upperclass
twit, totally useless.

ff9f1e5c-d070-4133-8192-025fe7a091d1.title: Draul Leptoc
ff9f1e5c-d070-4133-8192-025fe7a091d1.text:
If he threw a stone at the ground, he'd probably miss!
He's totally invisible when it's raining because he's so
wet!

998f7fa2-edf4-457a-8b09-a01ced2da652.title: <player>
998f7fa2-edf4-457a-8b09-a01ced2da652.text:
Well, I admit, he's probably not the sharpest knife in the
cutlery draw...

2f96e167-f67b-425b-a06e-9752fb49b279.title: Draul Leptoc
2f96e167-f67b-425b-a06e-9752fb49b279.text:
Sharp? I've seen keener wit in root vegetables. 
Anyway, stop changing the subject. Get out of here and
don't think you can sneak up those stairs to see Juliet,
because I'll catch you and then you'll be for it!

c3e58af0-8728-404c-bce5-f6f9d1887d59.title: Draul Leptoc
c3e58af0-8728-404c-bce5-f6f9d1887d59.text: Harsh but fair I think you'll find...now get OUT!

b6fd188f-091e-4aa9-9256-c9d8bfb0361f.title: <player>
b6fd188f-091e-4aa9-9256-c9d8bfb0361f.text: I've just come to have a chat with Juliet.

eac42e3b-b5a2-4e72-a4ce-25a39a10484e.title: Draul Leptoc
eac42e3b-b5a2-4e72-a4ce-25a39a10484e.text:
What on earth about? 
I hope you're not in cahoots with that good for nothing
Romeo!

e162423a-9280-42c2-9e8a-2b7921616609.title: <player>
e162423a-9280-42c2-9e8a-2b7921616609.text: Err..no of course not....why would I be?

173d3d9c-c3f8-4d9e-912b-c47dc4847af6.title: Draul Leptoc
173d3d9c-c3f8-4d9e-912b-c47dc4847af6.text:
He's been trying to wooo my daughter for an age.
Up until now she's had the good sense to just ignore
him. I just don't know what's gotten into her recently
so that she would give him the time of day.

25ee62a7-91fb-41d6-bea2-fff386d47d81.title: <player>
25ee62a7-91fb-41d6-bea2-fff386d47d81.text:
Well, love is mysterious! 
Perhaps one day someone may even learn to love you!

82823842-0e86-4d21-9869-542a63ad8a14.title: Draul Leptoc
82823842-0e86-4d21-9869-542a63ad8a14.text:
What! 
Someone may fall in love with me...what are you trying
to insinuate?

fb2afe16-6f8f-4cb8-8702-bdf625cb652d.title: <player>
fb2afe16-6f8f-4cb8-8702-bdf625cb652d.text: Err...Nothing....I guess I'd better be going now...

c7344183-287e-4309-ad62-adc7fd48cc34.title: Draul Leptoc
c7344183-287e-4309-ad62-adc7fd48cc34.text:
Just looking around! This is MY house! 
You might have at least 'ASKED' to view my
considerably well appointed abode...but no, you've just
burst in with all the elegance of a Troll at a tea party.

fcf53846-66fc-47aa-9107-262eb53612e0.title: <player>
fcf53846-66fc-47aa-9107-262eb53612e0.text:
I can see that you're busy ranting so I'll just nip off
and investigate a bit.

c64fb482-1d21-434e-b9f9-61a12322c4b6.title: Draul Leptoc
c64fb482-1d21-434e-b9f9-61a12322c4b6.text:
What are you doing in my house? Up to no good I
shouldn't wonder!

9b96d9aa-d675-4f8b-a3e8-72233f5925c1.title: <player>
9b96d9aa-d675-4f8b-a3e8-72233f5925c1.text:
Just a small chore for Juliet, you do have a lovely
daughter in her sir.

73317cad-2604-42a9-b7da-2acc6b5a5367.title: Draul Leptoc
73317cad-2604-42a9-b7da-2acc6b5a5367.text: Oh...why, thank you...I've always tried to my best...

0ac2d1e8-e6fd-42a0-b1c9-c2e95fc94756.title: Draul Leptoc
0ac2d1e8-e6fd-42a0-b1c9-c2e95fc94756.text:
...Hang on! Enough of that smiley talk. I have a
daughter and I know what she's like. Don't even think
of carrying on anything behind my back, I have the
eyes of a hawk, nothing gets past me!

01a1f85a-4ac7-4533-950a-df2447efa04f.title: Draul Leptoc
01a1f85a-4ac7-4533-950a-df2447efa04f.text:
Hey! What's that in your hands...looks like a message to
me...with Juliet's barely legible scrawl on it...

1047fd40-1cdd-44c0-8a4c-eb2cf483cd3d.title: <player>
1047fd40-1cdd-44c0-8a4c-eb2cf483cd3d.text: Yes, yes, that's probably why I can't read it!

bb79a4b4-3667-402f-94dc-735ebee818b7.title: <player>
bb79a4b4-3667-402f-94dc-735ebee818b7.text:
Sorry, I mean, that's right sir. I'm just popping to the
shops to get some groceries for Juliet.

b43aa537-e6b7-4210-a6d3-c6c6bbfeea98.title: <player>
b43aa537-e6b7-4210-a6d3-c6c6bbfeea98.text: Right, have to be off now...thanks...

f63f8659-a2a2-4b3c-9b12-d40965045312.title: Draul Leptoc
f63f8659-a2a2-4b3c-9b12-d40965045312.text:
Groceries!...at a time like this, does that girl know what
she's putting me through!

27cfb6db-1bdb-4fd1-a90f-b490222d3edd.title: Draul Leptoc
27cfb6db-1bdb-4fd1-a90f-b490222d3edd.text:
Do you live here? If so, how's about a couple of
hundred gold towards the rent eh? Pay your share I
say...you don't want to be like that freeloading Romeo!

9aff5b26-c679-4a8f-90e0-5bdaedde7ccd.title: Draul Leptoc
9aff5b26-c679-4a8f-90e0-5bdaedde7ccd.text: Hey, what are you doing here?

776d270d-0d11-42b8-b92b-8ea3f96a0a26.title: <player>
776d270d-0d11-42b8-b92b-8ea3f96a0a26.text:
Nothing much sir...I promise...I'm just an innocent
friend of Juliet's...doing her a few favours...as a friend.

d3b57ea4-18de-42a3-babb-3e929b269623.title: Draul Leptoc
d3b57ea4-18de-42a3-babb-3e929b269623.text:
Well, just make sure there's no funny business going
on that's all I can say. Do you know why?

6d6f1423-8377-4554-a8de-31273909b703.title: <player>
6d6f1423-8377-4554-a8de-31273909b703.text: I think I can guess sir...

14b6eed1-9643-435e-80c4-eae73e37a4f8.title: Draul Leptoc
14b6eed1-9643-435e-80c4-eae73e37a4f8.text:
There's no need to guess! You can see it in my hawk
like eyes, in my cat like ears and my dog like nose...

8d7f8cdd-8c70-42d6-b077-1c7dafbbd98d.title: <player>
8d7f8cdd-8c70-42d6-b077-1c7dafbbd98d.text: Are you saying that you look like an animal sir?

e98fefa0-375c-4210-9bbd-9829cd9c07b1.title: Draul Leptoc
e98fefa0-375c-4210-9bbd-9829cd9c07b1.text:
NO! Not look like an animal!
I have the keen 'SENSES' of an animal and I don't
miss a thing. Don't even think about trying anything!

3ec9d7e6-5c95-458d-bf47-15cc1e886576.title: Draul Leptoc
3ec9d7e6-5c95-458d-bf47-15cc1e886576.text:
Hey!
What's that in your hands?
Looks like some sort of potion to me!

37594849-7b88-40ce-9fff-41316a450fac.title: <player>
37594849-7b88-40ce-9fff-41316a450fac.text:
Err...no! Nope! Not a potion! 
Some medicine...I have a terrible cough 
...cough...cough....see?

bb2e873a-a813-47ef-b066-f549889f472c.title: <player>
bb2e873a-a813-47ef-b066-f549889f472c.text:
Except, I can't drink too much or else it makes me
feel 'really' tired. One sip of this and the lights go
out...I mean, I'm asleep in a minute.

f05ca6f8-6bd8-435d-b882-8a1109597aa3.title: Draul Leptoc
f05ca6f8-6bd8-435d-b882-8a1109597aa3.text:
Sleep...! How can you even think of such a thing at a
time like this? And I hope you have no intentions of
sleeping in my house!

c377370b-3fd5-4eb3-b951-fee0c31c9540.title: Draul Leptoc
c377370b-3fd5-4eb3-b951-fee0c31c9540.text:
You'll get a bill for rent if I catch you dozing off
around here!

9966ad93-224b-4c6c-8d73-d52879ba4ba4.title: Draul Leptoc
9966ad93-224b-4c6c-8d73-d52879ba4ba4.text:
My poor Juliet....she's dead...dead! I shouldn't have been
so hard on her...she was my lovely daughter. Booo
hoooo hooooo!

4e275163-2136-4202-bff7-0b2e614fbbd4.title: Draul Leptoc
4e275163-2136-4202-bff7-0b2e614fbbd4.text: I suppose you're quite pleased with yourself now...
